---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`About | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body style="background-color: #13151a; color: white; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;">
		<Header />
		<main style="max-width: 800px; margin: auto; padding: 2rem;">
			<h1 style="color: #D4AF37;">The Origin of Onero</h1>
			
			<div style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6;">
				<p>
					My name is Haitam—a name that translates to "eagle." The Onero identity and the sharp, steel-and-gold aesthetic of this domain are rooted in a lifelong brotherhood known as the <strong>Dark Knights</strong>. This site serves as the digital headquarters for my work.
				</p>
				
				<p>
					Beyond the lore, I am currently based out of Villeurbanne, where I specialize in Electronics, Telecommunications, and Computer Science. My technical focus ranges from low-level hardware design to web development. 
				</p>

				<h2 style="color: #D4AF37; margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 1.5rem;">Current Pursuits</h2>
				<ul style="list-style-type: square; padding-left: 1.5rem; color: #e0e0e0;">
					<li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><strong>Hardware & Code:</strong> Designing VHDL architecture (like Real-Time Clocks) and building web projects using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and Astro.</li>
					<li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><strong>Mathematical History:</strong> Tracing the origins of complex mathematical thought, scientific proofs, and the evolution of trigonometric functions.</li>
					<li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><strong>Optimization:</strong> Utilizing systems like Notion for interstitial journaling, tracking habits, and optimizing physical recovery and stamina in the pool.</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			
			<hr style="border-color: #333; margin: 3rem 0;" />
			
			<p style="text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #646464;">
				"Forged in the Dark Knights."
			</p>

		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>